1. *Razumemo* se bez reči. (We understand each other without words.)
2. Da li *razumete* šta govorim? (Do you understand what I'm saying?)
3. Oni *razumeju* samo svoje mišljenje. (They only understand their own opinion.)
4. Koliko ljudi *razume* važnost recikliranja? (How many people understand the importance of recycling?)
5. *Razumevši* vaše nezadovoljstvo, donećemo rešenje. (Having understood your dissatisfaction, we will find a solution.)
6. Nije teško *razumeti* zašto je toliko ljudi oduševljeno tim filmom. (It's not hard to understand why so many people are excited about that movie.)
7. Oni su veoma inteligentni, pa brzo *razumeju* nove koncepte. (They are very intelligent, so they quickly understand new concepts.)
8. Da li si *razumeo* šta sam rekao? (Did you understand what I said?)
9. *Razumevanje* tuđih perspektiva može biti ključno za rešavanje konflikta. (Understanding other people's perspectives can be crucial for resolving conflicts.)
10. Čini mi se da me niko ne *razume* u ovoj situaciji. (It seems like no one understands me in this situation.)